    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Privacy Policy for Notes & Reminders</h1>
            <div class="last-updated">
                Last updated: <span id="current-date">December 24, 2024</span>
            </div>
            <p>Thank you for using Notes & Reminders. We are committed to protecting your privacy.</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section>
                <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                
                <h3>Local Storage:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your notes and reminders are stored <strong>ONLY on your device</strong></li>
                    <li>We use Android's Room database for storage</li>
                    <li><strong>No data is sent to any external servers</strong></li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Voice Recognition:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>When using voice input, speech is processed by <strong>Google's speech recognition service</strong></li>
                    <li>We do <strong>NOT store or have access</strong> to your voice recordings</li>
                    <li>Voice processing follows <strong>Google's privacy policy</strong></li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Permissions:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Microphone</strong>: Only for voice input features (optional)</li>
                    <li><strong>Notifications</strong>: To show reminders</li>
                    <li><strong>Alarm</strong>: To schedule reminders</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use your information <strong>ONLY</strong> to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Store your notes on your device</li>
                    <li>Set reminders based on your instructions</li>
                    <li>Convert speech to text for voice input</li>
                    <li>Display notifications for reminders</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>All data is stored <strong>locally on your device</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>No data is transmitted</strong> to external servers</li>
                    <li>Data is protected by <strong>Android's app sandbox</strong></li>
                    <li>You can delete all data by <strong>uninstalling the app</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
                
                <h3>Google Speech-to-Text:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Used for voice recognition</li>
                    <li>Google's privacy policy applies: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Android System:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Uses Android's notification system</li>
                    <li>Uses Android's alarm scheduler</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have <strong>full control</strong> over your data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>View all notes in the app</li>
                    <li>Edit or delete any note</li>
                    <li>Clear all data by uninstalling</li>
                    <li><strong>No account required, no data collection</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>This app is safe for all ages:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>No personal information collected</li>
                    <li>No registration required</li>
                    <li>No inappropriate content</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>7. Microphone Permission (RECORD_AUDIO)</h2>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p><strong>Important:</strong> This app requests microphone permission <strong>ONLY</strong> for:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Voice-to-text functionality</li>
                        <li>When you explicitly tap the microphone button</li>
                        <li>Voice is processed by Google's secure services</li>
                        <li><strong>NOT stored or uploaded</strong> to any servers</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>You can use <strong>all other features</strong> without granting microphone permission.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Continued use of the app after changes means you accept the updated policy.</p>
